<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 | Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2f7 0%, #dee5ec 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #2c5a6e;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: #8fb3c2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2c5a6e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #6c7a8a;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn-back {
            background: #8fb3c2;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-back:hover {
            background: #769eae;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-help {
            background: white;
            color: #2c5a6e;
            border: 2px solid #8fb3c2;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-help:hover {
            background: #8fb3c2;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="error-code" style="text-decoration: underline dotted;">404</div> <br>
        <h1 class="error-title">Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</h1>
        <p class="error-message">Maaf, halaman yang Anda cari tidak tersedia.</p>
        
        <div class="button-group">
            <a href="#" class="btn-back" onclick="history.back()">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Kembali ke Beranda
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-help">
                <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Bantuan
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>